_sText:
Changes from original
changed some of the outside textures
at each tunnel ladder near ct spawn theres a lightswitch for the lights in the tunnel
in that underground area below the house theres a switch that only turns off all the switchable lights
theres a switch near the front door that turns them all on again
the pictures are func_breakable
the chairs and some smaller tables are physboxes
the toilets have breakable seats
32 instead of 14 spawnpoints

and a very big thank you to CunningStunt of www.sourceaddiction.com for fixing the ldr skybox problem

happy new years! go get drunk and shoot things
